<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="psi;4;435" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,6713;PEdg7;PSI4,435</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι χαίρειν Ζωίλος Ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σπέν</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ιο</unclear>ς τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶν </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="2"/>ὃς καὶ διασυνεστάθη σοι ὑπὸ τῶν τοῦ βασιλέως φίλων. ἐμοὶ σ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υμ</unclear>βέβηκεν 

    <lb n="3"/>θεραπεύοντι τὸν θεὸν Σάραπιν περὶ τῆς σῆς ὑγιείας καὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εὐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">η</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μερία</unclear>ς τῆς 

    <lb n="4"/>πρὸς <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic>τομ</sic></choice> βασιλέα Πτολεμαῖον τὸν <choice><corr>Σάραπίν</corr><sic>σαραπιμ</sic></choice> μοι χρημα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τίζει</supplied>ν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear>λε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νάκι</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐν τοῖς ὕπνοις, ὅπως ἂν διαπλεύσω π<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρὸς</unclear> σὲ κ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐμφ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ανίσω σοι τό</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νδε</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὸ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> 

    <lb n="6"/>χρηματισμόν, ὅτι δεῖ συντελεσθῆναι αὐτ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῶι</unclear> <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ τέμενος ἐν τῆι Ἑλληνικῆι πρὸς τῶι λιμέν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κα</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἱ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ερέα</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐπιστ</unclear>ατεῖν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αὶ</supplied> 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐπιβωμίζειν ὑπὲρ ὑμῶν. ἐμοῦ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δὲ</unclear> π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αιτησαμένου </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="9"/>ὅπως <choice><corr>ἄν</corr><sic>αμ</sic></choice> με παραλύσηι τοῦ ἐνταῦθ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἔργο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear>, εἰς <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀρρωσ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ία</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε πε</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ριέβα</unclear>λεν 

    <lb n="10"/>μεγάλην ὥστε καὶ κινδυνεῦσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αί</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">με</supplied>· <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">προ</unclear>σευξάμενος δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὲ</supplied> αὐ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τῶι, ἐ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ά</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν με</supplied> 

    <lb n="11"/>ὑγιάσηι, διότι ὑπομενῶ τὴν <choice><corr>λειτουργίαν</corr><sic>ληιτο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>ιαν</sic></choice> καὶ ποι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ή</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σει</supplied>ν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὸ</unclear> ὑφ᾽ αὑτοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/>προστασσόμενον. ἐπεὶ δὲ τάχιστα ὑγιά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σθ</unclear>ην, 

παρεγένετό τις ἐκ Κνίδου 

    <lb n="13"/>ὃς ἐνεχείρησεν οἰκοδομεῖν Σαραπιεῖον ἐν τῶι τόπωι τούτωι καὶ προσ-

    <lb n="14"/>αγηγόχει λίθους· ὕστερον δὲ ἀπεῖπεν αὐτῶι ὁ θεὸς μὴ οἰκοδομεῖν, καὶ <choice><corr>ἐκεῖνος</corr><sic>κακεινος</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="15"/>ἀπηλλάγη. ἐμοῦ δὲ παραγενομένου εἰς Ἀλεξάνδρειαν καὶ ὀκνοῦντός σοι 

    <lb n="16"/>περὶ τούτων ἐντυχεῖν, ἀλλὰ περὶ πραγματείας ἧς καὶ ὡμολογήκεις μοι, 

    <lb n="17"/>πάλιν ὑπετροπάσθην μῆνας τέσσερας <num value="4"/>· διὸ οὐκ ἠδυνάμην εὐθέως παραγε-

    <lb n="18"/>νέσθαι πρὸς σέ. καλῶς οὖν ἔχει, Ἀπολλώνιε, ἐπακολουθῆσαί σε τοῖς ὑπὸ τοῦ 

    <lb n="19"/>θεοῦ προστάγμασιν, ὅπως ἂν εὐίλατός σοι ὑπάρχων ὁ Σάραπις πολλῶι σε 

    <lb n="20"/>μείζω παρὰ τῶι βασιλεῖ καὶ ἐνδοξότερον μετὰ τῆς τοῦ σώματος ὑγιείας 

    <lb n="21"/>ποιήσηι. <add place="supralinear">σὺ οὖν</add> μὴ καταπλαγῆις <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del> τὸ ἀνήλωμα ὡς ἀπὸ μεγάλης σοι δαπάνης 

    <lb n="22"/>ἐσομένης, ἀλλ᾽ ἔσται σοι ἀπὸ πάνυ λυσιτελοῦντος· συνεπιστατήσω γὰρ ἐγὼ πᾶ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σι</unclear> 

    <lb n="23"/>τούτοις. 

    <lb n="24"/>εὐτύχει. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="25"/>Ζωίλου περὶ Σαράπιος. 

    <lb n="26"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="28">κη</num>, Αὐδναίου <num value="9">θ</num>, 

    <lb n="27"/>ἐν τῶι Βερενίκης 

    <lb n="28"/>ὅρμωι. 

    <lb n="25"/>Ἀπολλωνίωι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.694" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.694" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0257-02-13" type="textDate">vor 13. Febr. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.694" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Vgl. GRBS 41, 2001, S. 117-124.</p></div><div n="meta.694" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>verso Z. 2: <date type="mentioned" value="-0257-02-13">13. Febr. 257 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.694" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59034</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">694</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59034</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;1;59034" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.694" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">77</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">49</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">36</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.694